==English==

===Alternative usage===
Sometimes abbreviated as [[Abe Lincoln]].

===Etymology===
Derived from the name of the sixteenth [[president]] of the [[United States]], [[w:Abraham Lincoln|Abraham Lincoln]].

===Noun===
# A forthright and honest person.
#: ''What we need to restore faith in government is an '''Abraham Lincoln'''.''

